com.btc.redg.runtime.dummy

Interface DummyFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDummyFactory

    public interface DummyFactory
    The interface for RedG's dummy mechanism. When implementing a custom DummyFactory, getDummy(AbstractRedG, Class) has to return valid dummy entities. You should implement a way to recognize your generated dummy entities (preferably by keeping all dummies in a cache and then comparing against this cache), so that isDummy(RedGEntity) returns true for all dummy entities generated by your dummy factory and false otherwise.
